<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>setBodyText, given a string representing the mail body creates an instance of Zend_Mime_Part.
getBodyText returns this instance from which (if I'm not mistaken) only the encoded content can be recovered.
It would be good to have a method to recover easily the original text given to setBodyText.</p>

